    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RPGFan 上的 85%</strong> - <i>“它的英雄三人组 令人难忘，在引人入胜且详细的叙述中真正脱颖而出。特别是，这个十五个多小时的游戏的最后几个有趣的时间很快就过去了。“</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款角色驱动的日式角色扮演游戏中，探索古老宗教与科技融合的充满活力的世界。 掌握深度回合制战斗，用神圣魔法对抗带有机甲部件的野兽。 踏上一场伟大的冒险，取回与你的众神面对面所需的神圣巴别塔密码。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/a51006cbbb37148fa5c542e38f43a14a.poster.avif?t=1754918387\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/a51006cbbb37148fa5c542e38f43a14a.webm?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/a51006cbbb37148fa5c542e38f43a14a.mp4?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>扮演约什瓦·阿萨 (Joshwa Asa) 的角色，他是一名盲目崇拜神灵的士兵，濒临失去所受训练的一切。 为了让自己配得上他的上司，他承担了渗透敌方领土并获得神圣法典的使命，该法典可以使人类更接近他们的创造者。 但当长期埋藏的秘密被揭开，一个致命的邪教会不择手段地隐藏这些秘密时，乔什瓦必须质疑他的信仰，并在诸神发射大规模毁灭性火焰之前找到真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/740307886bffdf4ed5d27200ebac49f6.poster.avif?t=1754918387\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/740307886bffdf4ed5d27200ebac49f6.webm?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/740307886bffdf4ed5d27200ebac49f6.mp4?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>进入一个融合了奇幻和科幻小说精髓的异国情调，一切都通过古老宗教的镜头，以对犹太教和基督教以及古代巴比伦、苏美尔和埃及宗教的多年研究为后盾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/e01f39bba593ad3f665f3c76ceec3f4c.poster.avif?t=1754918387\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/e01f39bba593ad3f665f3c76ceec3f4c.webm?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/e01f39bba593ad3f665f3c76ceec3f4c.mp4?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>揭示敌人的弱点并使用神圣魔法消灭敌人。 使用同样的神圣魔法来增强你的力量并打破敌人的护盾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/920bdff6af6a8adea5fd126a1c48fcc1.poster.avif?t=1754918387\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/920bdff6af6a8adea5fd126a1c48fcc1.webm?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757890/extras/920bdff6af6a8adea5fd126a1c48fcc1.mp4?t=1754918387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>装备元素和神圣魔法，并为你的角色配备合适的武器和盔甲，以挑战和击败任何敌人，甚至是众神派来的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>已确认可在 Steam Deck 上使用！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
